OL,3,CAndy Burnham to meet devolved leaders
OL,4,Cfor first time as PM
OL,6,FAndy Burnham will meet with the
OL,7,Fdevolved leaders during his visit to
OL,8,FScotland for the Commonwealth Games.
OL,10,FIt's the first in-person meeting
OL,11,Fbetween the Scottish and UK leaders
OL,12,Fsince Mr Burnham became Prime Minister
OL,13,Fon Monday.
OL,15,FMr Burnham backs further devolution,
OL,16,Fbut both First Minister of Scotland
OL,17,FJohn Swinney and the First Minister of
OL,18,FWales Rhun ap Iorwerth, want
OL,19,Findependence for their countries.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/10
