OL,3,CAndy Burnham to meet devolved leaders
OL,4,Cfor first time as PM
OL,6,FThe new Prime Minister will arrive in
OL,7,FGlasgow on Thursday to watch the
OL,8,Fopening ceremony for the 2026
OL,9,FCommonwealth Games, where he will be
OL,10,Fjoined by the King and Queen.
OL,12,FThe UK Government has said Mr Burnham
OL,13,Fwould set out how he plans to work
OL,14,F"collaboratively" with devolved
OL,15,Fgovernments "based on a genuine
OL,16,Fpartnership".
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@QO]wD@MOUxD@LO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
