PN,43609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1784915311
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to meet devolved leaders
OL,4,Cfor first time as PM
OL,6,F"'Number 10 North' must not become
OL,7,Fjust Whitehall with a different
OL,8,Fpostcode. I agree wholeheartedly on
OL,9,Fempowering communities ` it's at the
OL,10,Fheart of my politics ` but decisions
OL,11,Faffecting Wales should be made in
OL,12,FWales, and it is for the Welsh
OL,13,FGovernment and our Senedd to work with
OL,14,Fthe people of Wales on how power is
OL,15,Fexercised and shared within our nation.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/10
